AWESOME MAP!!!!! 
Watch out where you step, the differently textured cubes are illusionary!! if you do TRIP, you will land in the water(FALL), which slowly damages you(DIE!!). there is a teleport, that will bring you up again, but your enemy might be camping there, waiting for you to appear......
soo....just don't drop :D
P.S.: look out for easter eggs, you might be able to surprise you enemy!! (tip: mp5.....) :D
